- Use the dev environment script in scripts/
- Before use, set the $NG variable to /path/to/neurogram in .bashrc
- Make sure to grab a copy of the .env file and store in react/
- Conda create then conda update the environment yml
- We're using MNE unstable version for Annotations.to_data_frame() ->
  instructions for install at bottom of environment yml
- lastly, npm -i in react/ and you should be off to the races